# Title: HackTool - Wmiexec Default Powershell Command
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-03-08
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the execution of PowerShell with a specific flag sequence that is used by the Wmiexec script
# MITRE Tactic: Lateral Movement
# Tags: attack.lateral-movement, attack.stealth
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_hktl_wmiexec_default_powershell.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

CommandLine="*-NoP -NoL -sta -NonI -W Hidden -Exec Bypass -Enc*"